Class PerformanceMeasuringProcess

  • java.lang.Object

        • fact.PerformanceMeasuringProcess
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    stream.Process

    public class PerformanceMeasuringProcess
extends stream.runtime.DefaultProcess
    This process is a replacement for the standard process from the streams library which computes statistics about the runtime of each processor it calls.

    You can use it like this:

    The output will be written to the json file specified by the url parameter.

    Created by Alexey and Kai on 27.05.15.
